#: ../../../release_details/9.5/ExplodeDataSet.md:1
msgid "Introduce vtkExplodeDataSet filter"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/ExplodeDataSet.md:3
msgid ""
"vtkExplodeDataSet creates a vtkPartitionedDataSetCollection from any input "
"dataset according to a cell scalar isovalue criteria. Each partition of the "
"output contains cells that share the same value for the given cell array."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/ExplodeDataSet.md:6
msgid ""
"It is similar to a vtkMultiThreshold, configured to extract every single "
"value of the input array."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/ExplodeDataSet.md:9
msgid ""
"It comes in replacement of vtkSplitByCellScalarFilter to use "
"vtkPartitionedDataSetCollection instead of vtkMultiBlockDataSet as output. "
"Also it relies on the threaded vtkExtractCells filter."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/ExplodeDataSet.md:13
